  Description: Church statue that has been abandoned for a very long time. Though
    can no longer distinguish good from evil, it never forgets its duty, continuing
    to bestow blessings upon those who seek for them.
  Skillset: "\u2022 Does not move and attack, immunes to crowd-controls, and does
    not count toward battle progress.\n\u2022 Increases the DEF and RES of all presenting
    enemies on the map.\n\u2022 While standing on a <color=green>Medical Tile</color>,
    transfers its healing effect to all presenting enemies on the map.\n\u2022 Upon
    defeat, heals your units once and grants them a permanent DEF buff."
